會做決定。<br />\n<br />\n你有6成民意？立法會比例代表制喎，你點玩都一定唔會夠配票機器嚟玩。當你直選好彩或者畀垃圾泛民做大台幫你配票攞半數喇，功能組別一定冇可能贏到，因為好多都係既得利益者或者團體票。<br />\n最後都係得一個結果，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">永遠都得唔到議會嘅決策權，最多只能夠得到否決權</span>。未計班人一定會用DQ同種票呢啲手段<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲人會問，制度內外一齊抗爭各有各做咪得囉，制度內嘅抗爭如果係有效嘅話就唔撚使出嚟用前途用條命同政府打啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">你哋而家係幫緊政府將抗爭由體制外帶返入體制內咋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你哋諗住血債票償嘅就早啲講啦，唔使犧牲幾千個手足呀，少幾百個被自殺同失蹤者你哋多幾百票添呀</span><br />\n<br />\n屌 個制度有問題你哋重陪佢玩係咪痴撚咗線呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNmjrV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNmjrV1.jpg&h=f7aa5a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我攞區選嚟比，兩邊嘅制度同玩法都唔同冇得比"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"政府正研究居內地港人投票安排<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=308412&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D308412%26refer%3DShare&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=8fd4eb7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D308412%26refer%3DShare&h=487b9a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=308412&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"38e9dd7763231c92e800bd16f800700996753349","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad36ab35f60e8bc87c757999d4dad1f576ec2aef","tid":1756443,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30f865c4c6b4c2a74fa72d7797d85e49be1769e","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"屌血債票償，但係身體卻很誠實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"要靜靜地win"},{"pid":"5efbb27a8b93d84a75dc6e7dde4861a183387492","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"港共政權啲手段有幾仆街大家應該好清楚<br />\n點解重要陪佢玩"},{"pid":"48d77613d0dcea581a1109072b20803183915170","tid":1756443,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 議會革命 七十議席 缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"320dc9cc853bf8d44b2e6f9da1f91514383dfbcb","tid":1756443,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb83005d94fbd5b9c1d11584a43bd4dc47c7ae03","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a10417603145b82ab3e4af365f5a3aacc7014053","tid":1756443,"uid":279866,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"要主攻功能組別"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"點攻都冇可能過到半數<br />\n我講多次，呢個係制度問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"尋日先見到有post話有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋可唔可以出少啲屌立法會研究post<br />\n出返啲真係制度外抗爭嘅post<br />\n而家連發起遊行post都唔見多個<br />\n屌人討論制度內抗爭嘅post就見到兩三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nplus如果唔同意制度內外雙線並行嘅話<br />\n根本啱啱果個區選都唔應該做，啲素人都唔應該去參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae83c55029209e264ad5bcd72b95c21fd64c440","tid":1756443,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"其實體制外同體制內兩條線一齊做無衝突架<br />\n---<br />\n區議會大捷係一個伏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756153</a>"},{"pid":"30bfa6387dc71701cc31febdaa9d347a810b6487","tid":1756443,"uid":15945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁大聲呀<br />\n又俾人屌分化L熱狗㗎啦"},{"pid":"648dfc31d20f7a291150f57b850b9b1a179f1410","tid":1756443,"uid":264400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8b49cbe23c7a281b671dd98e503f5dddec48c81","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"幫佢取消立法會選舉有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"區議會都可以做咁就可以永續嗰個抗爭熱度<br />\n不過身體卻很誠實"},{"pid":"962373d8f5591ce4cec2e223e72197e2eadf2a3f","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ae83c55029209e264ad5bcd72b95c21fd64c440","tid":1756443,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"其實體制外同體制內兩條線一齊做無衝突架<br />\n---<br />\n區議會大捷係一個伏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756153</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"前提係體制內抗爭係有效<br />\n前提係個制度係fair game"},{"pid":"5f434844db0aba21271129d19cb65cf62b7a2ba0","tid":1756443,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"學林鄭話齋 香港人和平選舉係希望社會和平<br />\n講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc32a201f15c399c3782ffc2a010294ea0dd8488","tid":1756443,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a10417603145b82ab3e4af365f5a3aacc7014053","tid":1756443,"uid":279866,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"要主攻功能組別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756451/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756451/page/1</a><br />\n投票建制阵营已经没有用, 因为选举不公正! 正如民建联与工联会所说, 选举已经被黄丝暴徒操控, 选举无法显示真正民意!!!<br />\n香港政府还说选举公平, 表示政府已经与暴徒及外国势力勾结, 操控选举, 分裂国家.<br />\n所以由今天起, 爱国人士应远离所有选举, 以免被扭曲的选举制度所代表!"},{"pid":"58238bdfe244f8b260a3a1d532fe1257186be32c","tid":1756443,"uid":289124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"320dc9cc853bf8d44b2e6f9da1f91514383dfbcb","tid":1756443,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb83005d94fbd5b9c1d11584a43bd4dc47c7ae03","tid":1756443,"uid":6033,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a10417603145b82ab3e4af365f5a3aacc7014053","tid"